OL,3,CIconic statue of Queen Victoria
OL,4,Ccovered in paint
OL,6,FAn iconic bronze statue commemorating
OL,7,FQueen Victoria's Diamond Jubilee has
OL,8,Fbeen vandalised.
OL,10,FThe protected monument in Candie
OL,11,FGardens was covered in pink paint or a
OL,12,Fsimilar substance sometime between 4pm
OL,13,Fon Wednesday 10 April and 8am on
OL,14,FThursday 11 April, police say.
OL,16,FA window on a nearby outbuilding has
OL,17,Falso been damaged.
OL,19,FOfficers are investigating and would
OL,20,Flike anyone with information to call
OL,21,Fthem on 01481 222222.
