OL,3,CIconic statue of Queen Victoria
OL,4,Ccovered in paint
OL,6,FThe structure is more than 21 feet
OL,7,Fhigh and has stood on public view for
OL,8,F124 years after Guernsey's Lieutenant-
OL,9,FGovernor unveiled it at a large
OL,10,Fgathering on 1 March 1900.
OL,12,FLocal people have reacted with anger
OL,13,Fon social media, describing the act as
OL,14,F"an utter disgrace", "absolutely
OL,15,Fdisgusting" and "so disrespectful".
OL,17,FBusinesses have offered to help clean
OL,18,Fthe monument for free.
